@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_cunusd(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = 0.74
    v1 = (v0 - (wp.cos(v0 + 0.26) - wp.exp(v0 + 0.27)))
    v0 = wp.sin(v0)
    v0 = 0.48
    v0 = ((wp.cos(v2 + 0.74) * tmp) / (wp.sin(v1 + 0.04) + 0.40))
    data[tid] = v0
